msgstr "`@BsonId` ：允许你自定义ID字段，见 link:#custom-ids[自定义ID] 。"

#. type: Plain text
#: upstream/_versions/1.11/guides/mongodb-panache.adoc:147
#: upstream/_versions/1.11/guides/mongodb-panache.adoc:298
